page.title: 14My Day,Marc Morley aged 10
page.content: A typical day for me is getting up at 07.45.Fot breakfast I have cereal toast and a cup of tea.I get ready for school at 08.00.At 08.30 I call for my friend Lee Arkley.We get to school at about 08.35.We play 5 a side football until 09.00.We have Assembly until 09.30.In the morning we do Maths until playtime at 10.30.At playtime I play football with my friends.We do English until 12.00.I have my dinner at school.At 13.15 we do something like Art or Topic.We have a break at 14.15.We go home at 15.30.At 19.15 I go to a church youth club.I play pooltable tennis and football.I go home at 21.00.I watch the T.V.,have some supper and go to bed at 21.30.
